txt.en: Wine can be found within Felegoth's wine cellar.\n\nYou should fetch some wine.
Wood Elves can be found in Felegoth.\n\nYou should give wine to Elves within Felegoth.
Hithlos can be found in Felegoth.\n\nYou should talk to Hithlos.
'Now, everyone is merry and my joyous music brings light into the cavern halls. I thank you. Please continue listening to my music for as long as you wish. You are a kind [placeholder].'
Many Elves live within the halls of Felegoth.\n\nYou should dance with some of the Elves.

'Do you feel the swell in the air and the cheer within these halls? Hmm, yes I also feel as though something more is missing. Perhaps the Elves could use some wine and dancing. I shall continue to play. If you would, make haste to the wine cellar in Felegoth and procure some wine for the Wood Elves.'
With harp in hand, Hithlos looks to lift people's spirits within the caverns of Felegoth.
